pull.title: [qa] Use cached utxo set to fix performance regression
pull.body:
I removed the caching in #9221, which made pruning take longer.

Credit goes to @morcos for quickly raising the issue: https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/9221#issuecomment-264683374

events.message: [qa] pruning: Use cached utxo set to run faster

events.body:
what about fixing maxuploadtarget.py 
i think it also got slower?
Not as significant, but gives back about 10 seconds, why not.
